  "body": "<div align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/BKw2JZQj/6f52c0ab982b253705acbb7296acb662.gif\" alt=\"NexusDev Network Banner\" width=\"100%\">\n  <br><br>\n  <p>\n    <a href=\"https://discord.gg/XhqAfHx7yE\">\n      <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/1263430459564621874?color=5865F2&label=Join%20our%20Discord&logo=discord&logoColor=white&style=for-the-badge\" alt=\"Join our Discord\">\n    </a>\n  </p>\n</div>\n\n<hr>\n\n<div align=\"center\" style=\"background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; margin: 20px 0;\">\n  <img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/kVNQvKGm/nexusdev-logo.png\" alt=\"NexusDev Network\" width=\"150\">\n  <h2>🎉 GRAND OPENING: NexusDev Network!</h2>\n  <p><b>Join our brand new Minecraft network!</b></p>\n  <p>Featuring cutting-edge custom gamemodes:</p>\n  <p>\n    <b>⚔️ Arc Raiders</b> | <b>🏛️ Civ 7</b> | <b>💀 SMP Hardcore</b> | <b>🤠 Wild West RP</b>\n  </p>\n  <p><b>Server IP:</b> <code>mc.nexusdev.cc</code></p>\n</div>\n# NexusMenus\nAn easy in-game GUI builder allowing different GUI types, rows and pages\n\n## Features\n- Different menu types (Chest, brewing stand, hopper, dispenser)\n- Customizable chest rows and pages\n- Customizable items\n- Item cooldowns\n- Item actions\n- PlaceholderAPI support\n- Customizable menu commands and permissions\n\n## Commands\n- /nexusmenus\n- /nexusmenus reload\n- /nexusmenus edit\n- /nexusmenus clearcooldown\n- /nexusmenus create",
